      "content": "that sounds like a good start. can u expand a bit more on the dress code part? like, if someone is attending a high-level business gala or a really fancy dinner, what are the specific clothing standards they should follow to be seen as truly professional and sophisticated? what would be the gold standard for their outfit?",
